<h3>News Archive</h3>

<div id="news-archive">

<p class="timestamp">11th February, 2011</p>
<h4>tomoyo-tools 2.2.0p2 and 2.3.0p1 released</h4>
<p class="article">New versions of tomoyo-tools for both the 2.2.x (<a href="../changelogs/tomoyo-tools-2.2.html.en">ChangeLog</a>) and 2.3.x (<a href="../changelogs/tomoyo-tools-2.3.html.en">ChangeLog</a>) branches have been released.</p>

<p>ChangeLog for tomoyo-tools 2.2.0p2:</p>
<pre>
Version 2.2.0p2 2011/02/11 Bugfix release.

  Mount sysfs when /sys/kernel/security/ does not exist rather than when /sys/kernel/ does not exist, for some distributions have /sys/kernel/debug/ on root device.
</pre>

<p>ChangeLog for tomoyo-tools 2.3.0p1:</p>
<pre>
Version 2.3.0p1 2011/02/11   Bugfix release.

  /sbin/tomoyo-init
    Mount sysfs when /sys/kernel/security/ does not exist rather than when /sys/kernel/ does not exist, for some distributions have /sys/kernel/debug/ on root device.
    Wait for /etc/tomoyo/tomoyo-post-init in a more reliable way.

  /usr/sbin/tomoyo-diffpolicy
    Fix regression introduced when fixing old/new inversion bug.
</pre>

